comments: Software License Maintenance.  The contract number 9202053201 in the original amount of $263,312.73 was created in the last quarter of 2012-2013 but was not disclosed on April 30, 2013 because it was being amended in April 2013.  The amendment was for additional licenses in the amount of $12,387.23, bringing the total value of the contract to $275,699.96.  This contract is a call-up against a Public Works and Government Services Canada procurement tool.
